    <svcsubproc>
        <title>RE Passenger Entry</title>
        <para>The RE entry step well is a forward body entrance utilizing swing out bifold aluminum entry doors. The
            step well entry is equipped with entry courtesy lights and step well area heater.
        </para>
        <para>The entry steps on the RE bus are lower profile, allowing for easier entering and exiting. The step well
            is equipped with assist handrails. The step assemblies are covered with a raised surface tread design. The
            step treads can be easily replaced when worn or damaged.
        </para>
